QuestData.Title: Putting An Eye Out
QuestData.Description: Ah! Wakener! You must help me! (You will help me, or else I will help myself to you!)$B$BI need more materials for my experiments, yes yes! (Blood and guts, hearts and brains, tongues and eyes, eyes, eyes!)$B$BTo the west, I have seen creatures of mist and fog. They possess such big, round, wonderful globes! Big for seeing, round and unblinking!$B$BGo now, little Wakener. Bring me back a single pristine eye!
